  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ffeffd319fd382447972467e83303c2a, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 864226267001
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of component factories. Enables production of machine parts, electronic components, precision tools, and more using refined metal ingots. Marks the beginning of mid-game production chains, providing essential materials for advanced buildings and vehicle production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267002
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of mines. Enables self-sufficiency in essential minerals including iron ore, coal, copper, gold, and aluminum. Requires high construction and maintenance costs, but provides the fundamental raw materials for industry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267003
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of chemical plants. Enables processing of crude oil into synthetic fabrics and chemical products. Serves as an alternative and complement to lumber mills, reducing wood dependency through petroleum-based fabric production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267004
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of heavy factories. Enables production of precision tools and premium products using advanced steel and cutting-edge components. Requires significant investment but targets the premium market to maximize profit margins.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267005
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of oil pumps. Enables extraction of crude oil from underground reserves. Marks the beginning of strategic resource self-sufficiency. Requires very high maintenance costs, but forms the foundation of chemical industry and fuel production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267006
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of smelters. Enables processing of raw ores mined from mines into refined metal ingots. Produces iron ingots, copper ingots, aluminum ingots, and more, providing essential intermediate materials for the metal industry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267007
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of engine factories. Enables production of high-performance internal combustion engines by combining machine parts, electronic components, and steel ingots. A prerequisite investment for vehicle production, beginning the production of high-value intermediate materials.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267008
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of military factories. Enables production of small arms, heavy weapons, ammunition, and more using steel ingots and machine parts. A national strategic resource, essential for war preparedness and dominating the weapons market.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267009
    m_Localized: Unlocks the construction of vehicle assembly plants. Enables production of the highest-value final products including cars, fighter planes, and tanks by combining engines, components, electronic parts, and more. The most complex and slowest production chain, but provides the highest profits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
